    #v(1fr)
    
    == The Brandbook
    
    This brand book serves as the ultimate guide to the visual and verbal identity of UP CURSOR. It establishes the core rules, components, and philosophy needed to communicate our brand consistently across all platforms. By adhering to these guidelines, we ensure that UP CURSOR remains distinct, professional, and instantly recognizable.
    
    #v(2em)
    
    == History
    
    Founded on August 16, 1983, the UP Association of Computer Science Majors (UP CURSOR) holds the proud distinction of being the oldest Computer Science student organization in the University of the Philippines. 
    
    Rooted in the UP Department of Computer Science within the College of Engineering, it has spent decades fostering academic excellence, technical proficiency, and strong bonds among its members. From organizing flagship events like the Computer Science Summit to spearheading community-driven initiatives, UP CURSOR has continuously evolved while staying true to its legacy of service and innovation.

    #v(1fr)
  ]
)

#pagebreak(weak: true)

#grid(
